                <expan><abbr>Numinib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Augustor</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Lucceius Marcellinus <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb von Z. 1 sind zwei weitere Zeilen modern eingehauen worden: &amp;quot;&amp;quot;MERCVRIO ET MINERVAE / ARNALIAE&amp;quot;&amp;quot;, sowie zwischen Z. 1 u. 2 &amp;quot;&amp;quot;SACRVM&amp;quot;&amp;quot; und Z. 2 u. 3 &amp;quot;&amp;quot;DECVR&amp;quot;&amp;quot;.</p>
            </div>
